## **ğŸ• PERKIRAAN WAKTU**

| Fase | Waktu | Output |
|------|-------|--------|
| Reconnaissance | 2-5 menit | Subdomain, URLs |
| Technology Analysis | 1 menit | Teknologi website |
| Parameter Discovery | 2-3 menit | Endpoint & parameter |
| Bug Scanning | 3-10 menit | Vulnerability findings |
| Security Headers | 30 detik | Security score |
| JS Analysis | 2-5 menit | Secrets & endpoints |
| **TOTAL** | **10-25 menit** | **Semua di atas** |

