## **ğŸ”§ TROUBLESHOOTING PER TOOL**

### **Jika `reconnaissance.sh` error:**
```bash
# Cek tools Go
which subfinder httpx

# Install jika missing
go install github.com/projectdiscovery/subfinder/v2/cmd/subfinder@latest
```

### **Jika Python script error:**
```bash
# Cek Python version
python3 --version

# Install requirements
pip3 install requests beautifulsoup4

# Jalankan dengan debug
python3 -m py_compile web_tech.py
```

### **Jika permission denied:**
```bash
chmod +x bughunter.sh reconnaissance.sh
chmod +x *.py
```

