## **ğŸ’¡ TIPS PAKAI TOOLS**

### **Untuk Target Besar:**
```bash
# Batasi scope
./bughunter.sh target.com
# Jika lama, tekan Ctrl+C, lanjut manual:
python3 bug_scanner.py target.com
```

### **Untuk Target Kecil:**
```bash
# Full scan cepat
./bughunter.sh testphp.vulnweb.com
```

### **Simpan Hasil:**
```bash
# Backup hasil
tar -czf hasil_scan.tar.gz output/target.com/
```

---

## **ğŸš€ COMMAND CHEATSHEET**

```bash
# INSTALL
git clone https://github.com/essev92-1/BugHunterFlow.git
cd BugHunterFlow
chmod +x *.sh *.py
pip3 install requests beautifulsoup4

# BASIC USAGE
./bughunter.sh target.com                    # Full auto
./reconnaissance.sh target.com               # Recon only
python3 bug_scanner.py target.com           # Scan bug only

# CHECK RESULTS
cd output/target.com/
ls -la
cat web_tech.json
cat bug_findings.json | jq '.'              # Pretty print JSON

# DEBUG
bash -x bughunter.sh target.com 2>&1 | tee debug.log
tail -f output/target.com/scan_*.log
```

